</div>

<h3 class="widget-title">Andrzej Piotrowski</h3></div></div><div id="panel-2-7-1-1" class="so-panel widget widget_sow-headline panel-last-child" data-index="17" ><div class="so-widget-sow-headline so-widget-sow-headline-default-967d82efc878 so-widget-fittext-wrapper" data-fit-text-compressor="0.85"><div class="sow-headline-container ">
<p class='sow-sub-headline'>Ekonomista, absolwent Szkoly Glownej Handlowej w Warszawie (1995), podyplomowe studia bankowosci w Graduate School of Banking at Colorado (2002).  Pracowal w bankowosci, dystrybucji i logistyce oraz finansach (controlling). Gra (nadal) w koszykowke, lubi jazde konna i strzelectwo.</p></div></div></div></div><div id="pgc-2-7-2"  class="panel-grid-cell" ><div id="panel-2-7-2-0" class="so-panel widget widget_sow-image panel-first-child" data-index="18" ><div class="so-widget-sow-image so-widget-sow-image-default-31c423e8ff7c">

<div class="sow-image-container">
<img src="http://www.spkin.edu.pl/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Adam_Szafranski-300x300.jpg" width="300" height="300" srcset="http://www.spkin.edu.pl/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Adam_Szafranski-300x300.jpg 300w, http://www.spkin.edu.pl/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Adam_Szafranski-150x150.jpg 150w, http://www.spkin.edu.pl/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Adam_Szafranski-768x768.jpg 768w, http://www.spkin.edu.pl/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Adam_Szafranski-1024x1024.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" title="Adam Szafranski" 		class="so-widget-image"/>
